{"tid":1302911,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"第一屆全民隻揪公開賽","createTime":"2019-07-10T06:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T15:14:22.000Z","uid":79351,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ca6a8bee787b619affd265049bc1ca3b3e4ed312","tid":1302911,"uid":79351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:10:21.000Z","msg":"日前有警員於旺角執行職務期間邀請市民隻揪<br />\n眾多市民反應熱烈表示要一齊應邀想同香蕉仔隻揪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有理由相信尋日警方full gear 搣走揪sir既海報係因為海報上無隻揪公開賽既任何資料<br />\n依d 行為係完全唔尊重警隊既邀請<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以小弟想借連登籌劃第一屆全民隻揪大賽<br />\n岩岩睇完場地<br />\n因伙伊館同紅館要7月中先知有無場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b7gGEPA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb7gGEPA.png&h=73d5da3f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uayhXBg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuayhXBg.png&h=46f7eab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果揀番旺角麥花臣場會唔會好d?<br />\n比賽規則跟mma 但不設磅數<br />\n相信依場公開賽緩和近日警民緊張既氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時需要搵人重新design 隻揪公開賽宣傳海報<br />\n另外，有無任何牌照要申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請大家一齊籌備隻揪公開賽"},{"pid":"1326206e8097110d625c28e3b4f7aaae3d9b9325","tid":1302911,"uid":50658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:10:51.000Z","msg":"召喚世清"},{"pid":"3fc9b61aa623558d028875fe5aa987f83a86898b","tid":1302911,"uid":79351,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:12:12.000Z","msg":"希望搵到Rex 參賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n贊助商搵寶礦力"},{"pid":"2df52420dc20b2024a1c71c59899de8dc9f624ac","tid":1302911,"uid":52760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:15:41.000Z","msg":"要搵邊個同香蕉糖一戰先<br />\n香蕉撚係唔係會上場先"},{"pid":"3a53111b757286cb22bcb22753dfa1e32ba40caa","tid":1302911,"uid":79351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s